    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a dream to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained, so it's totally ready for all your upcoming adventures! It drives beautifully and has plenty of life left in it. If you're looking for a reliable ride that you can count on, this is definitely the one. Feel free to reach out\u2014I'd love for you to come take it for a spin!",
