    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s example, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The longitudinal chassis has been properly sorted with a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed RTABs to handle the torque output of the factory limited-slip differential. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, and the suspension geometry remains tight thanks to Bilstein dampers and updated bushings. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the powertrain remains robust with consistent compression across all cylinders and a linear power delivery up to the 7,900 RPM redline. This is a performance-first vehicle for an enthusiast who values mechanical integrity and analog feedback.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
