    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a well-maintained 2016 Lexus GX 460 that perfectly balances executive luxury with legendary off-road capability. The Starfire Pearl exterior retains a deep, brilliant shine; however, in the interest of full transparency, there are a few minor stone chips on the front hood and a small, shallow scuff on the rear bumper from city parking. The interior is a smoke-free environment featuring supple parchment leather. While the driver\u2019s seat bolster shows light, age-appropriate creasing, the cabin remains tight and rattle-free. All technological features\u2014including the Mark Levinson premium audio, navigation, and heated/ventilated seating\u2014are fully operational. Mechanically, this vehicle is robust. It comes with a comprehensive service history detailing regular oil changes and milestone maintenance. The 4.6L V8 engine runs quietly, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and the 4WD system engages without hesitation. The tires currently have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes were serviced within the last 5,000 miles. This is an honest, reliable SUV that has been cared for with an open checkbook and is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
