      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for this absolute gem of a car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape\u2014it runs like a dream and has been super well-maintained! Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, it's ready for plenty more adventures. It's got a lot of life left in it and is just waiting for the right driver. Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
