    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the S54B32 high-revving 3.2L inline-six engine. This driver-focused example is equipped with the Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and the factory M-Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque distribution. Essential preventative maintenance is complete, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The chassis retains its sharp handling characteristics via a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry. While the exterior shows minor age-appropriate patina, the powertrain remains potent, delivering linear acceleration to its 8,000 RPM redline. A solid, analog performer ready for the open road.",
